name: Bren Quersey
Lore: 'Piloted Red 8 at the Battle of Yavin. Dreamed of attending the prestigious Raithal Academy. Trained on X-wings by Wedge Antilles.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to anything he pilots. When piloting Red 8 during battle, adds one destiny to total power only. When at Raithal system, adds 1 to each of your Force drains there.',
